1 (3) The Auditor may promulgate administrative regulations in accordance with KRS
2 Chapter 13A to establish the application process and documentation necessary
3 for an entity to qualify to be included as a scholarship granting organization on
4 the list maintained under subsection (2) of this section.
5 (4) The Auditor may enter into agreements with other state agencies to assist in
6 implementing this section.
